    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a practical option for anyone needing reliable transportation without the premium price tag of a newer model. The exterior shows clear signs of its history, including several noticeable scratches, small door dings, and some fading on the roof's clear coat. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows moderate wear and some staining consistent with regular use over the years. Mechanically, the car starts and runs reliably, though it may require some routine maintenance or minor repairs in the near future to keep it in peak operating shape. It is a solid, functional car that has been used well and still has plenty of life left for the right owner.",
