    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty. I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, it is in stunning condition! It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously cared for, and honestly feels like it just left the dealership. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been truly babied and is ready to hit the road today, this is the one! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is an exceptional specimen of the final naturally aspirated M-division flagship, powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 paired with a precise 6-speed manual transmission. The mechanical integrity is absolute, featuring documented rod bearing and throttle actuator services to ensure peak operational reliability. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and an M-variable differential lock, delivering telepathic turn-in and superior lateral stability. Finished in concours-level Interlagos Blue, the exterior retains its factory depth, including a flawless carbon fiber roof with zero UV clear-coat degradation. Inside, the Novillo leather remains supple and free of bolster wear, reflecting a collector-grade environment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
