    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a breathtaking example of automotive preservation, presented in a condition that can only be described as showroom-perfect. The exterior paint retains a deep, glass-like luster, free from any swirl marks, stone chips, or blemishes, thanks to a professional-grade ceramic coating applied early in its life. Every body panel aligns with factory precision, and the alloy wheels are entirely devoid of curb rash, wrapped in a set of premium, high-performance tires with nearly full tread. Inside, the cabin feels like a time capsule; the hand-stitched leather remains supple and matte, showing no signs of the typical bolsters wear or creasing. The interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma, and every electronic feature\u2014from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist displays\u2014operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a meticulous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified technicians. This car has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never been exposed to inclement weather. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a truly flawless vehicle.",
      "price": 47500.0,
